{"tid":1346340,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[停止圍爐、立即Connect 中間派同藍絲] 請大家落各僆儂牆廣傳元朗政警鄉黑既合作！！！","createTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T12:19:31.000Z","uid":283449,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"afa4f5d4ec77a797b8bdb4517f7947c57c498c6f","tid":1346340,"uid":283449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T03:59:03.000Z","msg":"元朗呢單野係千載難逢既機會，俾我地爭取翻之前漸失既民意。<br />\n但呢單野 CCTVB 只係用左 30秒報導，而且播出黎既都係黑白均勢格劍既情況。<br />\n打記者、大肚婆流產完全冇報，亦都冇報導 999 cut 線、警局落閘、件事同何妖既關係。<br />\n<br />\nCCTVB 唔報唔緊要，我地報！<br />\n唔好淨係網上圍爐打飛機。<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>僆儂牆唔係淨係用黎守，每日好多人睇僆儂牆既野，我地係可以用黎發放有用資訊，去打輿論戰。</strong></span></span><br />\n將社會既荒謬、政警鄉黑既合作廣傳開去！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n僆儂牆度如果有人望落有興趣了解多 d，唔該主動 d 行過去講解。<br />\n我之前試過做反送中，真係有唔少人黎問我野。<br />\n<br />\n如果各兄弟o係網上見到有好既文宣，麻煩o係呢度分享。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08e79cb404cf8c0ced4e8624227eda05d84353da","tid":1346340,"uid":39205,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:15.000Z","msg":"幫手推，宜家係關鍵時期動搖淺藍民意！<br />\n<br />\n【文宣重點】元朗上環兩條戰線一齊推<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345788\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345788</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"6a25cf5342c365f36294793dfc90061fe24ec50d","tid":1346340,"uid":194403,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:00:45.000Z","msg":"廣傳"},{"pid":"8f61639bd575daa27ab489bfd6217cf8b2139fdc","tid":1346340,"uid":283449,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T04:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o0LmMmj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo0LmMmj.jpg&h=a1e415f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZFpZx1k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZFpZx1k.jpg&h=52e442ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img